## **ðŸ”¹ Core Development Principles**
- **Build Features Incrementally**
  - Each feature should be developed and tested independently.
  - Components should be modular and reusable.
- **Test Components in Isolation**
  - Unit tests should cover core logic and UI components.
  - API endpoints should be tested separately before full integration.
- **Follow Agile Sprint Structure**
  - **Phase 1:** AI JD Generator & AI CV Generator (MVP Features)
  - **Phase 2:** AI Hiring Insights, AI Career Transition, & Workflow Automation
  - **Phase 3:** Monetization & Growth
- **Document All Major Changes**
  - Every major feature addition should have proper documentation.
  - PRD should be updated when core functionalities change.
- **Maintain Version Control Standards**
  - Use `git commit` messages that clearly describe changes.
  - Regularly push updates to GitHub (`git push origin main`).

